								<h2>Ethical Management</h2>
							</div>
							<div class="sec_txt">
								<p class="txt1">Aiming at shared value through<br>customer-centered management.</p>
								<p class="txt2">SM Group has created the Code of Conduct as the standards of behaviors and value which all members shall observe to contribute to the nation and society through Creating Shared Value (CSV) for greater value as a reliable partner for customers and partners and a pleasant workplace for employees and officers built on customer-centered management. </p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="sec_inner2 sec_inner">
							<h3 data-motion="bgType1">Practice 4 Steps</h3>
							<ol class="practice_lst" data-motion="staggerType1">
								<li data-role="m_elm">Clearly defined the ethical value of company and designed the specific guidelines for conduct.</li>
								<li data-role="m_elm">Specifically stated the personal responsibilities and duties for ethical behaviors.</li>
								<li data-role="m_elm">Constructed an internal control system to supervise the customs.</li>
								<li data-role="m_elm">Established the procedure to reinforce ethical behaviors and punish unethical behaviors.</li>
							</ol>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
