							</div>
							<div class="sec_txt">
								<p class="txt1">Pursuing righteous decision-making<br>based on ethical values.</p>
								<p class="txt2">Ethical training is the fundamental and essential element of ethical management. It teaches how you should deal with ethical issues. SM Group raises members’ ethical awareness through ethical training programs and ensures that they make decisions and act based on ethical values.</p>
							</div>
